data.description:
This beautiful one story corner home is a newly renovated property with easy access to shopping, Hwy 183 & other amenities. This community is quiet and perfect for families. The backyard is large and amazing for all animals! 

Property is currently being occupied but will be available by the 24th of October.

The property has three bedrooms and one and a half bathrooms and is only 20 minutes away from Copperas Cove and 29 minutes away from Fort Hood. Pets allowed with non refundable deposit. Refrigerator and microwave will convey with the property. New 6 foot privacy fence has been added into backyard. Under the carport there is also a washer and dryer hookup. Utilities not included.

Renter responsible for all utilities. Security deposit of $300 and prorated rent due before at lease signing. Rent is $1575. Cats have a non refundable deposit of $100 and dogs will have a non refundable deposit of $150. No smoking allowed indoors. Painting and hanging items on the walls is allowed. Tenants are responsible for maintaining lawn monthly and will have a $60 fee included in rent amount if not maintained properly.
